canonical:
  title: 次杻城公館壁上韻
  author: 兪升旦
  language: lzh
  text: 再過煩宵候松明道兩傍䏶槍新翼衛腰劒舊顔行共待寒年纊誰分儉歲粱酌民無小澤每愧勸鵝黃
  rtl: true
  vertical: true
lzh_formatted:
  title: 次杻城公館壁上韻
  author: 兪升旦
  language: lzh
  text: 再過煩宵候。松明道兩傍。䏶槍新翼衛。腰劒舊顔行。共待寒年纊。誰分儉歲粱。酌民無小澤。每愧勸鵝黃。
korean:
  title: 유성공관에서 벽상의 시에 차운하여
  author: 유승단
  language: kor
  text: |-
    두 번 찾아오니 저녁 행차 맞느라고
    관솔횃불이 길 양쪽에 환하구나
    어깨에 창을 멘 것은 새로 뽑힌 위졸들
    허리에 칼 찬 이는 구면이로세
    추운 겨울 솜옷을 모두 기다리는데
    흉년의 찹쌀은 누가 나눠 줄소냐
    백성들에게 조그만 덕택도 없었으니
    아황주 권할 때마다 부끄럽기 그지없네
  url: https://db.itkc.or.kr/dir/item?itemId=BT#dir/node?dataId=ITKC_BT_1365A_0120_010_0440&viewSync=OT
  footnotes:
  - key: '[주-D001] 아황주 : '
    value: 거위새끼 빛의 담황색(淡黃色) 술.
english:
  title: Responding to a Poem on the Wall of the Yuseong Governor's Residence
  author: Yu Seung-dan
  language: eng
  text: |-
    Twice now I come to greet the evening procession,
    And torches of pine flare bright on either side of the road.
    New recruits stand watch with spears upon their shoulders,
    While veterans in old regalia wear their swords at the hip.
    We all await the quilted robes against winter's cold,
    Yet who will distribute the rice when the harvest fails?
    I have bestowed so little kindness upon the people,
    So shame overwhelms me each time I offer them yellow wine.
  footnotes:
  - key: ''
    value: The 'yellow wine' (아황주) mentioned in the final couplet is a pale yellow liqueur, its color compared to that of gosling down. The image suggests the insufficiency of such meager offerings when the people's material needs go unmet.
